      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00017"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168815">Wien XVIII. Sternwartestrasse 71</rs></hi></addrLine></address><address><addrLine><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00016"/><hi rend="latintype">Herrn Dr. Richard Beer Hofmann</hi></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb68">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb235251">Hasenauerstr 59</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg type="letterhead"><seg rend="left"><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00018"/><hi rend="pre-print">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></seg><seg rend="right"><date when="1910-11-03">3/11 910</date></seg></seg><seg type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">Wien XVIII. <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L01977-1"/>Spoettelgasse 7<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L01977-1">Schnitzler verwendet das nicht mehr aktuelle
                           Briefpapier.</note></rs>.</hi></seg><salute>lieber Richard,</salute></opener><p>für den »<rs ref="#pmb40063" type="org">Mutter<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chutz</rs>« ka<c rendition="#gemination-n">nn</c> ich nicht le<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en – weil ich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>on<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t auch für<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o u<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>oviel
               andre Vereine le<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en müßte, <pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00019"/>die mich<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon
               aufgefordert haben u noch auffordern werden; u. weil ich überhaupt in <rs ref="#pmb50" type="place">Wien</rs> nicht gern le<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e.</p><p><rs ref="#pmb26392" type="person">Leo</rs> ni<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>ts mir
               gewi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>s nicht übel.</p><closer><pb facs="1910_AS_RBH_2_00019"/>Herzlich<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Ihr<lb/><signed>A.</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
